	e learned in Unexpected Productions’ Improv School.\\n\\n\\n\\nJoin us ton
	ight at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater for the Winter Student Show
	case! \\nWatch as our talented students—ranging from beginner to advanced 
	levels—take the stage to craft spontaneous\\\, engaging\\\, and often hila
	rious improv scenes right before your eyes. Our 300\\\, 400\\\, and 500-le
	vel students will showcase their newly honed skills\\\, giving you an excl
	usive preview of the next generation of improv stars. \\nYou’ll experience
	 a variety of performance styles inspired by UP’s mainstage shows\\\, maki
	ng for an unpredictable and highly entertaining night. Stick around after 
	the show to meet the performers—you’ll be able to say\\\, “I saw them befo
	re they were famous!” \\n6:00pm: Chad Sunday 300\\\, Bestock 400\\\, Tim 4
	00\\\, Tony 500\\n8:00pm: Chad Monday 300\\\, Chazz 400\\\, Laurel 400\\\,
	 Liz 500 \\nDon’t miss this chance to support our rising improv stars and 
